Description: Bindings to 'libpoppler':
    A tool for extracting text, fonts, attachments and metadata from a PDF file.
    Also supports high quality rendering of PDF documents into PNG, JPEG, TIFF
    format, or into raw bitmap vectors for posterior processing.
